Le Baltikane chhiba si [[chhib|chhiba]] le Baltikane selyange, ekh familyorri andar i familiya le [[Indo-Europikane chhiba|Indo-Europikane chhibyange]]. Kadale chhiba si labyarde kai [[Baltikani rig]] ([[Nordutni Europa]]). But vakyarne le akanutne baltikane chhibange si andar le thema [[Lituaniya]] thai [[Latviya]].

==Xulavipen==
Kadaya familiya chhibavipnaski xulavdyovel pe dui riga:

*Ovestutne baltikane chhiba
**[[Galindani chhib]] †
**[[Purani Prusikani chhib]] †
**[[Sudovikani chhib]] †

*Estutne baltikane chhiba
**[[Latvikani chhib]] (vai Letonikani chhib)
**[[Lituanikani chhib]]
**[[Selonikani chhib]] †
**[[Semigalikani chhib]] †

(†—Xasardi, muli chhib)

